                <h3>Our History</h3>
                <p>Founded in 2020, Multitools was born out of the desire to create functional, stylish clothing for everyday wear. We believe that fashion should be accessible, versatile, and built to last. Starting as a small online brand, we quickly expanded into a global presence, offering high-quality apparel for a variety of lifestyles.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="mission" class="about-section">
                <h3>Our Mission & Vision</h3>
                <p>Our mission is to provide clothing that meets the highest standards of quality and reflects the values of sustainability and inclusivity. We aim to redefine modern fashion by creating timeless pieces that are both functional and fashionable, becoming a global leader recognized for our commitment to quality, innovation, and social responsibility.</p>
